metadata.title: Quick fit Wubba Water Resistant Furniture, Universal Car Seat, Couch Cover, Convertible Platform Bridge Backseat Protector, and More for Dogs and Cats, 45" W x 34" L, Sage-Chocolate
features: SLEEP SURFACE: The Quick fit Furniture Cover features a fun and complementary dual color scheme in its reversible design. Simply flip the protector over to your desired shade to mix and match with your existing furniture.

PROTECT YOUR FURNITURE: Both sides of the cover boast water-resistant pinsonic fabric quilting, which not only adds a bit of extra padding for comfort, but also provides quality protection against spills and accidents.

BOLSTERED COMFORT: Snuggly soft quilted sleep surface is completed by matching back and side bolsters made with 100% recycled fluffy fill. They provide additional nestling comfort and optimum snuggles for your beloved pet.

FASTEN SECURELY: The cover comes with cushion anchors to properly fasten against the furniture. This installation measure keeps the cover from shifting to provide proper protection against accidents and pet debris.
description: Made of a soft faux suede, they're water, soil, and snag resistant, so they can easily handle your family mishaps. Just throw them in the washing machine when necessary, put them back on your furniture, and your room will be ready for the next movie night!
